OASISFormat: 0.4
Name:        zstd
Version:     0.2
Synopsis:    Bindings to zstd compression library
Authors:     ygrek
Copyrights:  (C) 2016 ygrek
License:     BSD-3-clause
Plugins:     DevFiles (0.3), META (0.3)
BuildTools:  ocamlbuild
Homepage:    https://github.com/ygrek/ocaml-zstd

Description:
  Zstd, short for Zstandard, is a fast lossless compression algorithm,
  targeting real-time compression scenarios at zlib-level compression ratio.
  .
  See http://zstd.net/ for more info
  .
  This library provides OCaml bindings.

Library zstd
  Path: src
  Modules: Zstd
  InternalModules: Zstd_stubs, Zstd_generated
  CClib: -lzstd
  BuildDepends: ctypes.stubs
  CSources: zstd_cstubs.c, zstd_ocaml_stubs.c

Executable zstd_gen
  Install: false
  Path: src
  CompiledObject: best
  MainIs: zstd_gen.ml
  BuildDepends: ctypes.stubs

Executable test
  Install: false
  Build$: flag(tests)
  Path: test
  MainIs: test.ml
  CompiledObject: best
  Custom: true
  BuildDepends: zstd, extlib

Test test
  Command: $test

Document api
  Title: API reference
